{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2623630/extras/wishlist_1-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1731297674\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Exoforge is a cooperative Sci-fi action game where players band together to explore unique worlds, and mine vital resources while engaging in thrilling third-person combat against diverse NPC enemies. Use what you gather to craft tools, items, gear, upgrades, and power-ups. Need a ride? Get behind the wheel with your squad in customizable vehicles to traverse rough terrains and take the fight to the enemy or resources back to base! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With seamless drop-in/drop-out multiplayer, Exoforge is the co-op experience you have been waiting for! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2623630/extras/explore_1-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1731297674\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Grab a vehicle and explore beautiful alien worlds on the hunt for precious resources. Beware, you are not the only one on the planet and the locals may not take kindly to you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2623630/extras/friends_1-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1731297674\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Bring a pal or a few! Drop in and out seamlessly with up to 6 of your friends. Work together to take down hordes of enemies that scale to the number of players in your party. Chat, trade, and share easily with your squad! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2623630/extras/gather_1-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1731297674\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you want it, craft it! Defend and gather resources as quickly as possible before the enemy notices. Craft weapons, gear, upgrades, and power-ups to get the edge on the enemy or just look awesome! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2623630/extras/customize_1-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1731297674\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Tailor your whole vibe! Find that perfect look by customizing your character, weapons, gear, and vehicles to create a style as unique as yours! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Play Your Way</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Don't stress about the grind. Hop in and out with friends and play at your own pace! Engage enemies in various ways, become the party healer, or focus on mining. The world is yours and how you interact with it is too!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2623630/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731297674","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2623630/page.bg.jpg?t=1731297674","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2623630/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1731297674","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2623630/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1731297674","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[1,5],"notes":"Mature content will include killing humanoid alien races with guns and melee weapons. Player characters can be nude with exposed genitalia and wearing revealing outfits. Animated emotes can be sexually implicit. In certain areas of the game, players will be able to see naked NPCs or NPCs in r